prerequisites:
-zig 0.15.2 packages
-devkitpro 3ds packages
-hardware, i never used citra so i cant advise if it works there too or doesnt... probably does



compilation:

Go in your project root:

# Clean build
> zig build

#streaming to your homebrewed console [set your console's IP adress into build.zig]
> zig build deploy
